{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Raider of Realms</strong> is a 2D real-time strategy game played on a hexagonal grid. Begin your adventure with a few tiles under your control and gather valuable resources to grow your kingdom. Build units, develop an army, and strategically conquer new tiles to expand your empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297620/extras/Banner2Compressed.gif?t=1740344945\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players must manually place humans and units on the right tiles to collect resources, defend their land, and fight enemies. Success depends on your ability to manage your resources and territory efficiently while fending off opposing forces. Are you ready to become the raider of realms?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297620/extras/Banner1Compressed.gif?t=1740344945\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hexagonal grid</strong>: Play on a map made of hexagonal tiles allowing for interesting gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Procedural generated worlds</strong>: Play on countless unique worlds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">25+ different units to defeat and create to make an huge army.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Resource management:\u00a0Collect resources from your controlled tiles to build and maintain your kingdom.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3297620?t=1740344945","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297620/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740344945","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steams